        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "input",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " schema. It captures various details related to a project change, such as project identifiers, agency codes, facility information, budget details, and savings metrics. After inserting the record, it updates the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "ProjectChange",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table to reflect the modification date and user, and it also updates the status of related scenarios in the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "budget.Scenario",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
